# Plan: "No Instruments, No Flight: The Enterprise Agentic Imperative"

Standalone executive thought leadership piece (~3500 words) for CTO/VP Engineering audiences. Conversational tone, Mermaid diagrams with descriptive captions, fully self-contained.

